═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ STREAM-α : F1-CLOSURE-FINALIZATION ← DETAIL
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  § α1 : T3-D15 LET-GENERALIZATION INTEGRATION
    loc    : cssl-hir/src/{env.rs, infer.rs, typing.rs}
    scope  :
      TypeScope Ty → Scheme .holds-polymorphic-types
      check_let : ty_of_bind → generalize .at let-boundary
      Path use-site : Scheme → instantiate .fresh-vars
      retire : Ty::Param(Symbol) skolem .legacy
      guard  : env-free-var-collection .correct (no-quant .env-bound)
    tests  : ~15-20 covering :
      let-poly : `let f = λx. x in (f 1, f true)` type-checks
      monomorphic : still-works (rank-0 scheme)
      env-bound : not-generalized (classical HM counter-case)
      instantiation-freshness : two-uses distinct-vars
      rank-1-only : nested-scheme rejected w/ helpful error
    est.   : 1 commit • ~500 LOC + ~20 tests

  § α2 : MACRO-HYGIENE WALKER
    loc    : cssl-hir/src/macro_hygiene.rs (NEW)
    scope  :
      structural-walker .mirroring ad_legality + ifc + staged_check
      diagnostic-codes :
        MAC0001 UnregisteredMacroInvocation
        MAC0002 HygieneAnnotationOnNonMacro
        MAC0003 TierMismatch (@hygienic .on tier-1 attr-macro)
      stage-0 ≡ shape-only ← full hygiene = T8-phase-2 scope
      HIR lacks scope-set tracking ∴ walker-validates declaration-shape
    tests  : ~10-12 covering 3-diagnostic-codes + positive-paths
    est.   : 1 commit • ~600 LOC + ~12 tests

  § α3 : PROOF-CERT EMISSION + R18 SIGNING .of SMT-VERDICTS
    loc    : cssl-examples/src/ad_gate.rs + cssl-smt/src/lib.rs
    scope  :
      SmtVerification :
        + query_text : String
        + solver_stdout : Vec<u8>
      SignedProofCert {
        query_hash : [u8; 32],
        verdict_hash : [u8; 32],
        solver_kind : SolverKind,
        timestamp_ns : u64,
        payload_hash : [u8; 32],
        signature : [u8; 64]
      }
      append .SignedProofCert → AuditChain .tagged smt-verdict
      verify_attestation : payload_hash-match + signature-verify + chain-append
    tests  : ~8-10 sign+verify-roundtrip + tamper-rejection
    est.   : 1 commit • ~350 LOC + ~10 tests

═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ STREAM-β : KILLER-APP BROADENING ← DETAIL
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  § β1 : AnalyticExpr VECTOR-EXTENSION
    loc    : cssl-examples/src/ad_gate/analytic.rs
    scope  :
      + AnalyticExpr::Vec3(Box<A>, Box<A>, Box<A>)
      + AnalyticExpr::Dot(Box<A>, Box<A>) .lowers-to sum(a_i * b_i)
      + AnalyticExpr::Length(Box<A>) .lowers-to sqrt(Dot(v, v))
      + AnalyticExpr::Normalize(Box<A>) .lowers-to v / Length(v)
      simplify + evaluate + to_smt + to_term extended
    tests  : ~8 per-op smoke + composition
    est.   : 1 commit • ~400 LOC + ~10 tests

  § β2 : sphere_sdf + scene_sdf GATES
    loc    : cssl-examples/src/ad_gate.rs
    scope  :
      add ReferenceGateCase {
        sphere_sdf(p: vec3, r: f32) = length(p) - r
      } .w/ analytic-grad :
        ∂/∂p sphere_sdf = normalize(p)
      add scene_sdf(p) = min(sphere_sdf(p, 0.5), sphere_sdf(p - ..))
      gate : 3-way verification .per scalar-cases
    tests  : ~5 canonical-points
    est.   : 1 commit • ~300 LOC + ~8 tests

  § β3 : MONOMORPHIZATION-PASS .for vec3
    loc    : cssl-mir/src/monomorph.rs (NEW)
    scope  :
      vec3 generic-struct specialization
      call-graph-driven instantiation
      name-mangling : cssl$vec3$<elem>
      emit specialized MIR-bodies
    tests  : ~12 covering specialization + call-site-rewriting
    dep    : β1 + β2 complete-first
    est.   : 2 commits • ~1500 LOC + ~15 tests

  W! β3 = optional-stretch .if-time ← β1+β2 sufficient .for claim-broadening

