    scope  :
      TraceExporter + MetricsExporter trait-impls
      gRPC : tonic-client .against OTLP-collector
      HTTP : reqwest .POST protobuf .to /v1/traces
      batching + retry-policy + backoff
    tests  : ~10 encode+dispatch-roundtrip + offline-fallback
    est.   : 1 commit • ~800 LOC + ~12 tests

