    scope  :
      @hot_reload_preserve attr-annotation
      HIR-pass .identifies-preserve-boundaries
      state-migration plan-emission .for runtime
    tests  : ~8 attr-recognition + boundary-identification
    est.   : 1 commit • ~400 LOC + ~10 tests

  § γ5 : 12 ORACLE-BODIES
